 0.9999999999704414, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Finance & Development\", \"types\": [\"Q737498\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finance_&_Development\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finance_&_Development\"}, {\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Kisan_Samman_Nidhi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Kisan_Samman_Nidhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Kisan_Samman_Nidhi\"}, {\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Kisan_Samman_Nidhi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Kisan_Samman_Nidhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Kisan_Samman_Nidhi\"}, {\"begin\": 2373, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Fasal_Bima_Yojana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Fasal_Bima_Yojana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Fasal_Bima_Yojana\"}, {\"begin\": 2373, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Fasal_Bima_Yojana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Fasal_Bima_Yojana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pradhan_Mantri_Fasal_Bima_Yojana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Accredited social health activists (ASHA), auxiliary nurse midwives (ANM) and anganwadi workers; elected women representatives; beneficiaries of Sankalp: Hub for Empowerment of Women, Lakhpati Didi and Drone Didi initiatives and Sakhi Kendra scheme; and workers of Child Welfare Committees and district child protection units also witnessed the ceremony.\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2499, \"end\": 2503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.267035267272123e-25, \"text\": \"ASHA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2532, \"end\": 2535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Macau_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.073279706303408e-24, \"text\": \"ANM\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Macau_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Macau_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2671, \"end\": 2675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mamata_Banerjee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.552554180184939e-33, \"text\": \"Didi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mamata_Banerjee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mamata_Banerjee\"}, {\"begin\": 2698, \"end\": 2704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawkgirl\", \"score\": 0.9992037565537509, \"rank\": 0.0007968525024315751, \"text\": \"Kendra\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawkgirl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawkgirl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One guest from each block of the aspirational blocks programme, workers of the Border Roads Organisation, students from PRERANA School programme, and sarpanches of panchayats which achieved saturation in priority sector schemes were there as well.\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2898, \"end\": 2923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Border_Roads_Organisation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Border Roads Organisation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Border_Roads_Organisation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Border_Roads_Organisation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gathering comprised nearly 2,000 people from various states and union territories dressed in their traditional attire also attended the grand ceremony.\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Besides, 3,000 winners of different online competitions, organised by the Defence Ministry in collaboration with MyGov and Akashvani, were part of the celebrations.\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3298, \"end\": 3314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Defence_(Russia)\", \"score\": 0.44611810995295426, \"rank\": 0.7995925642985533, \"text\": \"Defence Ministry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Defence_(Russia)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ministry_of_Defence_(Russia)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 2,000 boy and girl cadets (from Army, Navy and Air Force wings) of the NCC from different schools across the country participated in the celebrations.\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3433, \"end\": 3437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Army\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.145671328769071e-20, \"text\": \"Army\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Army\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Army\"}, {\"begin\": 3439, \"end\": 3443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Navy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4727320592267153e-14, \"text\": \"Navy\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Navy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Navy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These cadets were seated on Gyanpath, opposite the ramparts.\", \"from\": 3552, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They formed 'My Bharat' logo with customised tricolour kits.\", \"from\": 3613, \"to\": 3673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3629, \"end\": 3635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.78950940716734e-35, \"text\": \"Bharat\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 500 National Service Scheme (NSS) volunteers also took part.\", \"from\": 3675, \"to\": 3746, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3690, \"end\": 3719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Service_Scheme\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Service Scheme (NSS)\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Service_Scheme\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Service_Scheme\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Published- August 15, 2024 08:46 am IST  customs and tradition/government/Independence Day  Copyright\\u00a9 2025, THG PUBLISHING PVT LTD. or its affiliated companies.\", \"from\": 3748, \"to\": 3909, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 3930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"BACK TO TOP  Terms & conditions|Institutional Subscriber  Comments have to be in English, and in full sentences.\", \"from\": 3932, \"to\": 4044, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They cannot be abusive or personal.\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please abide by ourcommunity guidelinesfor posting your comments.\", \"from\": 4081, \"to\": 4146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have migrated to a new commenting platform.\", \"from\": 4148, \"to\": 4194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are already a registered user of The Hindu and logged in, you may continue to engage with our articles.\", \"from\": 4195, \"to\": 4305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4